### Basic scenario
## State-based alarm: Pushing the button once switches the screen on with a Hello World message.
## Pushing it again switches it off.

application screenHelloWorld

# Declaring bricks
sensor button: 9
actuatorLCD lcd: 1
actuator buzzer: 11
actuator led: 12

# Declaring states
on {
    buzzer <= HIGH
    buzzer <= LOW
    lcd : BuzzerOn <= TRUE
    lcd : LedOff row 1 <= TRUE
    button is HIGH =>  step
}

step {
    buzzer <= LOW
    led <= HIGH
    lcd : BuzzerOff <= TRUE
    lcd : LedOn row 1 <= TRUE
    button is HIGH => off
}

-> off {
    led <= LOW
    buzzer <= LOW
    lcd <= FALSE
    button is HIGH => on
}
